description: Ever wanted to be able to tell your own jokes to Alexa instead of just listening to hers?  Now you can with Joke Responder.  You can start either a 'knock knock' joke or a simple question joke and Alexa will play along.  A lot of fun for everyone.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Joke Responder for 'knock knock'
Why did the chicken cross the road?
What did one snowman say to the other?
name: Joke Responder
shortDescription: You can tell Alexa jokes and have her play along
